"Bosnian Olympic Committee President: Firmly Believes China has the Ability to Host Winter Olympics during Special Times - Xinhua News Agency" 
"Serajevo, December 11th, Xinhua News Agency - The President of the Bosnian Olympic Committee, Kwevcevic, recently expressed that Bosnia is highly anticipating the Beijing Winter Olympics, and firmly believes that China has the ability to host the Winter Olympics during special times." 
"Recently, the Chinese ambassador to Bosnia, Jiping, met with the President of the Bosnian Olympic Committee, Kwevcevic, at the Sarajevo Olympic Center." 
"During the meeting, Kwevcevic actively evaluated the relationship between Bosnia and China and expressed that he visited China during the 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics and was deeply impressed by China's excellent organizational work. He firmly believes that China has the ability to host the Winter Olympics during special times. Bosnia is highly anticipating the Beijing Winter Olympics and the Bosnian Olympic Committee is actively organizing participation. Bosnia hopes to use this as an opportunity for wider exchanges and cooperation in the field of sports with China." 
"Jiping stated that Bosnia and China have a special "Olympic tie."
"The 1984 Sarajevo Winter Olympics was successfully held here and in two months, the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics will also begin, presenting a simple, safe, and exciting event to the world." 
"Expecting the two countries to deepen exchange and cooperation in the preparation of winter sports events, athlete training, etc., the Chinese Embassy in Bosnia and Herzegovina is willing to continue to play a bridge role and take advantage of the Beijing Winter Olympics to promote the deepening of cultural exchanges between the two countries, let the people of the two countries "move forward together" and wish Bosnian and Herzegovinian athletes good results in Beijing." 
"Before the meeting, the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee held the "10th Annual Best Athlete" award ceremony, with Ambassador Ji Ping as a special guest to award the best young athlete in Bosnia and Herzegovina." 
"The Beijing Winter Olympics promotional video was played on loop at the event."